// Album: Similarity Gradient
// Track: 19 — quiet-mutation
// Target similarity: 18/100
// Actual similarity: 41.3/100
// Similarity band: moderately similar
// Concept: A quiet mutation — pick() drives a Markov walk through unfamiliar scale degrees on n().
// Musical strategy: pick + n + scale combination is rare in the repo; minimal effect chain.
// Strudel focus: pick(), n(), scale() — all together with no stack.
// Visualisation: ._pianoroll({ cycles: 8, smear: true }) — smear traces the walk.

n(pick(rand, [0, 2, 5, 7, 8, 11]))
  .scale("a:minor")
  .legato(0.3)
  ._pianoroll({ cycles: 8, smear: true })
